messages.content: Привет! Я готов к работе. Чем я могу помочь вам с проектом Gemini CLI?

thoughts.subject: Considering a Greeting
thoughts.description: I've decided on a simple Russian greeting: "Здравствуйте!". Following this, I'll succinctly confirm my readiness to help with their Gemini CLI project. Keeping it short and sweet seems the best approach for an effective initial response.
